title: Easy German
description:
Hallo Leute,
this is Janusz and Cari from Berlin. Together with our friends we produce Easy German, a show to help you learning the German language and getting to know Germany. We provide two free new videos for you each week, one on Wednesday, being aimed at beginner levels (A1 - B1) and one on Sunday, being aimed at more advanced levels (B1 - C1).
To deepen your learning experience with Easy German, we invite you to become a member of Easy German on Patreon (www.patreon.com/easygerman) and receive interactive exercises, transcripts and further extras for our videos on a weekly level.
We are also part of Seedlang, an awesome web-app that helps you learn German from scratch with interactive video flashcards that help you aquire grammar, vocabulary and pronounciation in a fun and entertaining way: www.seedlang.com
